without your approval.

314
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:43,152
(The ninth day of the fifth month,
3th year of Xuantong era)

315
00:22:43,152 --> 00:22:44,832
(two days before Mangzhong)

316
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:06,920
