321
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,000
Men Sandao.

322
00:23:23,359 --> 00:23:25,039
Do you really betray the court?

323
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,400
Haven't I already told you before?

324
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:30,440
What about the Dharma Seal?

325
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:32,160
You got it?

326
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:34,240
Do you remember the day

327
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:35,319
when Liu Lin and I

328
00:23:35,319 --> 00:23:36,880
could enter the Futu Temple
but you couldn't?

329
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:39,519
Liu Lin saw the letter left
by my master.

330
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,759
In 1851, Prajna, Bodhi,

331
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:44,640
and Dharma met for the thirty-year pact.

332
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:46,839
But the chief of Disciplinary Department
didn't appear.

333
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,519
So the three chiefs made a deal.

334
00:23:48,519 --> 00:23:50,000
To avoid accidents,

335
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:52,480
they tattooed their respective patterns

336
00:23:52,519 --> 00:23:54,079
on their disciples' bodies

337
00:23:54,319 --> 00:23:55,359
to pass them down.

338
00:23:56,079 --> 00:23:56,839
Wang Jialuo.

339
00:23:57,039 --> 00:23:59,480
The Dharma Seal has been on you.

340
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:01,359
What about Lin Haohan?

341
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:03,920
He is Prajna's inheritor.

342
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:10,039
Though Lin Haohan has died,

343
00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:12,519
Prajna's inheritors are about to arrive.

344
00:24:13,279 --> 00:24:14,440
We are here

345
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:15,880
waiting for them.

346
00:24:40,799 --> 00:24:43,480
The chief of the Prajna Hall
spread revolutionary ideas overseas.

347
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:44,559
He has many disciples.

348
00:24:44,559 --> 00:24:46,079
Each of them

349
00:24:46,079 --> 00:24:47,440
bears the Prajna Seal.

350
00:25:03,319 --> 00:25:04,200
Hi, thank you for coming.

351
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:04,759
Hello.

352
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:07,680
Hello.

353
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:08,704
Hello.

354
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:12,079
I have already copied the tattoo on you.

355
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,400
Again,

356
00:25:13,519 --> 00:25:14,400
I admire you.

357
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:15,839
Join us.

358
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,480
If you want to talk,

359
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,799
I'll talk to you about the revolution.

360
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,880
At first,
you may be reluctant to listen.

361
00:25:21,359 --> 00:25:22,319
If you listen more,

362
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:23,920
you will gradually accept it.

363
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:41,960
I'd rather die.

364
00:25:46,359 --> 00:25:47,160
Men Sandao.

365
00:25:48,119 --> 00:25:49,359
Let's fight.

366
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:50,759
Why?

367
00:25:51,039 --> 00:25:52,160
You haven't eaten for days.

368
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:53,240
You can't even stand steady.

369
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:54,559
Can you be my opponent?

370
00:25:55,759 --> 00:25:57,279
Let's fight.

371
00:25:59,559 --> 00:26:00,359
Alright.

372
00:26:01,079 --> 00:26:02,359
Let's see what you can do.

373
00:26:04,039 --> 00:26:04,880
I'm telling you.

374
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,039
I'm not in a hurry.

375
00:26:06,039 --> 00:26:06,839
I can wait.

376
00:26:06,839 --> 00:26:07,839
I can gradually influence you.

377
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:08,720
When I'm tired,

378
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,759
I will tie you up

379
00:26:09,759 --> 00:26:11,119
and throw you into the Futu Temple.

380
00:26:11,119 --> 00:26:12,160
After some years,

381
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,359
you will understand

382
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,519
why we need a revolution

383
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,839
and why we must change the nation.

384
00:26:57,759 --> 00:26:59,839
The ancients have made it clear.

385
00:26:59,839 --> 00:27:00,799
Once rules are established,

386
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:02,240
why should they be changed?

387
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:09,200
I do my best to chase the criminal

388
00:27:09,839 --> 00:27:11,839
not only to uphold the law
and regulations

389
00:27:12,839 --> 00:27:14,039
but also to motivate myself.

390
00:27:28,079 --> 00:27:29,559
I, Wang Jialuo,

391
00:27:35,519 --> 00:27:36,880
fail the court.

392
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:38,440
(A nation needs a ruler.)

393
00:27:39,079 --> 00:27:40,480
I let down the people.

394
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,519
(A court needs rules.)

395
00:27:42,119 --> 00:27:44,079
I fail the emperor.

396
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:45,952
(Constable of Dagu County Yamen)
The law needs to be upheld.

397
00:27:46,799 --> 00:27:48,799
I fail to fulfill my duty.

398
00:27:49,119 --> 00:27:51,079
(A minister cannot be
without integrity.)

399
00:27:54,079 --> 00:27:55,640
Do I have a reason

400
00:27:56,799 --> 00:27:58,279
to live in this world?

401
00:28:08,200 --> 00:28:10,279
Wang Jialuo.

402
00:30:12,759 --> 00:30:13,680
Can you read it?

403
00:30:15,319 --> 00:30:17,400
Lin Haohan has told me the way

404
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,319
to decode the seal.

405
00:30:21,519 --> 00:30:23,359
The Discipline Seal appears
like mountains and waters.

406
00:30:23,359 --> 00:30:25,960
In fact, it refers to Mount Huangmei

407
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:26,960
and Caoxi.

408
00:30:29,839 --> 00:30:32,000
The Dharma Seal is a field of reeds,

409
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:34,599
suggesting the story
of crossing the river by a reed.

410
00:30:34,599 --> 00:30:36,599
Therefore, the message conveyed
by the seal

411
00:30:36,599 --> 00:30:37,640
is two places, Guangzhou

412
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:40,240
and Songshan Shaolin Temple.

413
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:48,480
The Bodhi Seal signifies the starting
and ending points of the treasure.

414
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,880
Tianzhu is the starting point.

415
00:30:50,359 --> 00:30:53,640
And the Southern Shaolin burnt down
300 years ago

416
00:30:53,839 --> 00:30:54,720
is the end.

417
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:58,640
Therefore, the three seals

418
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:00,799
indicate six locations.

419
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:02,759
Tianzhu,

420
00:31:03,119 --> 00:31:03,880
Southern Shaolin,

421
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,200
Guangzhou,

422
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,200
Songshan Shaolin Temple,

423
00:31:07,039 --> 00:31:08,079
Mount Huangmei,

424
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,400
and Baolin Temple of Caoxi.

425
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:21,319
The Prajna Seal is an amulet,

426
00:31:21,319 --> 00:31:22,640
implying guardianship.

427
00:31:22,839 --> 00:31:24,599
So the central point
of the six locations...

428
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:33,160
Tianzhu and Baolin Temple of Caoxi,

429
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:38,599
Songshan Shaolin Temple
and Southern Shaolin,

430
00:31:41,599 --> 00:31:43,640
Mount Huangmei and Southern Shaolin,

431
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:47,160
Baolin Temple of Caoxi
and Southern Shaolin.

432
00:31:51,839 --> 00:31:53,200
So, that's how this works.

433
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,079
Here.

434
00:32:30,839 --> 00:32:33,079
Master asked us to guard this place.

435
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:35,920
I never thought

436
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:38,559
that we'd been guarding the entrance

437
00:32:38,559 --> 00:32:39,720
to the Altar Treasure.

438
00:32:42,359 --> 00:32:43,960
It's been guarded for generations.

439
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:49,240
What we've been guarding
is the secret treasure.

