496
00:36:24,519 --> 00:36:25,719
The other is for Wang Jialuo.

497
00:36:27,119 --> 00:36:28,360
Without them,

498
00:36:28,559 --> 00:36:30,480
we wouldn't have the chance
to open the Altar Treasure.

499
00:36:31,159 --> 00:36:32,440
The number of tombstones

500
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,360
doesn't matter.

501
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:37,000
So many have died.

502
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:40,360
We don't even know who they are.

503
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:44,928
By the way,

504
00:36:46,079 --> 00:36:48,039
where are you two heading next?

505
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:52,360
Are you returning to the capital?

506
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:53,856
No.

507
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:57,760
My place is just a birdcage
made of gold.

508
00:36:58,960 --> 00:37:00,360
I finally flew out of it.

509
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,639
Why do I fly back?

510
00:37:05,760 --> 00:37:06,304
And you?

511
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:10,719
Before leaving the capital,
I was a fourth-ranked imperial guard.

512
00:37:10,719 --> 00:37:13,280
Now I have become an accomplice
of rebels.

513
00:37:13,639 --> 00:37:14,719
Can I go back?

514
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:16,559
To be precise,

515
00:37:17,239 --> 00:37:19,239
