516
00:37:20,239 --> 00:37:22,400
How can you see yourself
as an accomplice?

517
00:37:25,559 --> 00:37:27,199
Where are we two going?

518
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,480
I'll go to Hong Kong.

519
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,639
Lin Haohan's fellows

520
00:37:31,639 --> 00:37:33,639
are transporting the treasures.

521
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:36,039
I am responsible for supervising.

522
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:38,039
If I go with you,

523
00:37:38,039 --> 00:37:39,199
I won't be of much help, right?

524
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,559
You go to Wuchang.

525
00:37:43,079 --> 00:37:44,119
My friends

526
00:37:44,519 --> 00:37:45,639
and comrades are there.

527
00:37:47,039 --> 00:37:48,440
When I come back from Hong Kong,

528
00:37:48,719 --> 00:37:49,559
I will come to find you.

529
00:37:55,199 --> 00:37:55,712
Okay.

530
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:58,000
I will wait for you.

531
00:38:00,239 --> 00:38:01,719
You find a place

532
00:38:01,719 --> 00:38:04,000
for us to stay.

533
00:38:04,679 --> 00:38:06,719
I prefer a western-style house.

534
00:38:07,679 --> 00:38:08,199
Okay.

535
00:38:09,159 --> 00:38:10,519
I will plant flowers in the yard.

536
00:38:10,719 --> 00:38:11,880
Red spider lilies.

537
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:18,239
Can I go with you?

538
00:38:19,079 --> 00:38:20,320
I'm tired of slaughtering pigs.

539
00:38:20,599 --> 00:38:22,280
I might as well join you
in the revolution.

540
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:25,039
After all, I'm good at killing beasts.

