546
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:54,360
the Wuchang Uprising succeeded.

547
00:38:54,679 --> 00:38:56,039
I'll be at a loss too.

548
00:38:56,639 --> 00:38:57,239
Succeeded?

549
00:38:58,679 --> 00:38:59,960
Isn't it a victory?

550
00:39:01,159 --> 00:39:03,599
I think it is just the beginning.

551
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:05,440
Now it depends on the power of the army

552
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,360
to change the situation.

553
00:39:07,119 --> 00:39:08,039
This is just one city.

554
00:39:09,119 --> 00:39:10,239
To change a country,

555
00:39:10,239 --> 00:39:11,920
it takes more people to wake up.

556
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:13,519
Hello?

557
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:15,159
The revolution in Wuchang will ignite.

558
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,360
I'm not sure if it can spread

559
00:39:17,599 --> 00:39:19,639
throughout the country
or can truly change the nation.

560
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:20,960
I hope it can.

561
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:24,280
But given the experiences
over the past years, I think

562
00:39:24,599 --> 00:39:25,320
we have to change

563
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:27,199
by completely
overthrowing the feudal dynasty.

