573
00:39:40,519 --> 00:39:41,760
I believe in this.

574
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:42,760
I am willing to go on.

575
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,519
Muqing, what are you saying?

576
00:39:47,639 --> 00:39:49,280
Hello, can you hear me?

577
00:39:50,119 --> 00:39:51,280
I can hear now.

578
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,119
I'm saying the day

579
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:56,480
