580
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:57,599
will come.

581
00:39:57,599 --> 00:39:58,800
The day when I marry you

582
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,039
will come too.

583
00:40:03,519 --> 00:40:04,480
Wait for me.

584
00:40:33,376 --> 00:40:35,246
(August 29, 1913)

585
00:40:35,246 --> 00:40:37,636
(Men Sandao died
in the Second Revolution in Nanjing.)

586
00:40:37,636 --> 00:40:39,726
(October 10, 1926)

587
00:40:39,726 --> 00:40:41,296
(Wulan Shan followed the Fourth Army
of the Northern Expedition)

588
00:40:41,296 --> 00:40:43,496
(and was shot by a stray bullet
during the general attack in Wuchang,)

589
00:40:43,496 --> 00:40:44,960
(and died in Guangzhou one year later.)

590
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:52,858
(Since they parted in Fujian,
they've never met again)

591
00:40:54,976 --> 00:40:59,072
(The End)

